---
// About.astro
---
<section id="mission" class="mission" aria-labelledby="mission-heading">
  <div class="mission__inner section-inner">
    <div class="mission__panel">
      <div class="mission__top">
        <h2 id="mission-heading">Your voice. Your way.</h2>
        <img src="/assets/mission-infinity.png" alt="" aria-hidden="true" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
      <p>
        We are building TYPE to create innovative, adaptive typing support for nonspeaking autistic
        people to grow communication skills and be heard.
      </p>
      <a href="#mission-overlay" class="btn">Our Mission</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div id="mission-overlay" class="overlay" aria-label="Mission and what TYPE is">
  <div class="overlay__card">
    <h3 class="overlay__title">Mission &amp; What TYPE Is</h3>
    <div class="overlay__body">
      <p>
        TYPE is a co-designed adaptive typing project for nonspeaking autistic people and their
        supporters. It provides communication-focused tools, participatory research, and practical
        pathways to shape future prototypes.
      </p>
      <p>
        TYPE is not therapy. It is a communication and autonomy support project designed with users,
        not for users.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="overlay__actions">
      <a href="#journey" class="btn">Get Updates</a>
      <a href="#footer-involved" class="btn">Get Involved</a>
    </div>
    <a href="#mission" class="overlay__close" aria-label="Close mission overlay">Close</a>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .mission {
    background: var(--color-surface-alt);
    color: #0d0d0d;
    padding-block: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .mission__panel {
    border: 0.0625rem solid #777;
    border-radius: 2rem;
    padding: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2.5rem);
    display: grid;
    gap: 1rem;
    max-width: 61.25rem;
  }

  .mission__top {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
    gap: 1rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .mission__top img {
    width: min(16.875rem, 30vw);
    object-fit: contain;
  }

  .mission__panel h2 {
    font-size: clamp(2.1rem, 6vw, 3.4rem);
    line-height: 1;
    max-width: 26.25rem;
  }

  .mission__panel p {
    color: #222;
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 2.4vw, 1.25rem);
    max-width: 43.75rem;
  }

  .mission__panel .btn {
    width: fit-content;
    color: #0c0c0c;
    border-color: #0c0c0c;
  }

  .mission__panel .btn:hover,
  .mission__panel .btn:focus-visible {
    background: #0c0c0c;
    color: #fff;
  }

  @media (max-width: 47.5em) {
    .mission__top {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .mission__top img {
      width: min(13.75rem, 52vw);
    }
  }
</style>
